#. <section id="vagga"><section class="sutta" data-uid="an1.31" id="31"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an1.31-40:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 1"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 1"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an1.31-40:0.2"
msgid "4. Adantavagga"
msgstr "4. Wild"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an1.31-40:0.3"
msgid "31"
msgstr "31"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc31.1"></a>
msgctxt "an1.31-40:31.1.1"
msgid ""
"“Nāhaṃ, bhikkhave, aññaṃ ekadhammampi samanupassāmi yaṃ evaṃ adantaṃ mahato "
"anatthāya saṃvattati yathayidaṃ, bhikkhave, cittaṃ."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, I do not see a single thing that, when it’s not tamed, is so "
"very harmful as the mind."

msgctxt "an1.31-40:31.1.2"
msgid "Cittaṃ, bhikkhave, adantaṃ mahato anatthāya saṃvattatī”ti."
msgstr "A wild mind is very harmful.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an1.31-40:31.1.3"
msgid "Paṭhamaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p></article></section><section class="sutta" data-uid="an1.32" id="32"><article><div class="hgroup"><h1>
msgctxt "an1.31-40:31.1.4"
msgid "32"
msgstr "32"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc32.1"></a>
msgctxt "an1.31-40:32.1.1"
msgid ""
"“Nāhaṃ, bhikkhave, aññaṃ ekadhammampi samanupassāmi yaṃ evaṃ dantaṃ mahato "
"atthāya saṃvattati yathayidaṃ, bhikkhave, cittaṃ."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, I do not see a single thing that, when it is tamed, is so very "
"beneficial as the mind."

msgctxt "an1.31-40:32.1.2"
msgid "Cittaṃ, bhikkhave, dantaṃ mahato atthāya saṃvattatī”ti."
msgstr "A tamed mind is very beneficial.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an1.31-40:32.1.3"
msgid "Dutiyaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p></article></section><section class="sutta" data-uid="an1.33" id="33"><article><div class="hgroup"><h1>
msgctxt "an1.31-40:32.1.4"
msgid "33"
msgstr "33"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli1.7"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc33.1"></a>
msgctxt "an1.31-40:33.1.1"
msgid ""
"“Nāhaṃ, bhikkhave, aññaṃ ekadhammampi samanupassāmi yaṃ evaṃ aguttaṃ mahato "
"anatthāya saṃvattati yathayidaṃ, bhikkhave, cittaṃ."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, I do not see a single thing that, when it’s not guarded, is so "
"very harmful as the mind."

msgctxt "an1.31-40:33.1.2"
msgid "Cittaṃ, bhikkhave, aguttaṃ mahato anatthāya saṃvattatī”ti."
msgstr "An unguarded mind is very harmful.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an1.31-40:33.1.3"
msgid "Tatiyaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p></article></section><section class="sutta" data-uid="an1.34" id="34"><article><div class="hgroup"><h1>
msgctxt "an1.31-40:33.1.4"
msgid "34"
msgstr "34"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc34.1"></a>
msgctxt "an1.31-40:34.1.1"
msgid ""
"“Nāhaṃ, bhikkhave, aññaṃ ekadhammampi samanupassāmi yaṃ evaṃ guttaṃ mahato "
"atthāya saṃvattati yathayidaṃ, bhikkhave, cittaṃ."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, I do not see a single thing that, when it is guarded, is so "
"very beneficial as the mind."

msgctxt "an1.31-40:34.1.2"
msgid "Cittaṃ, bhikkhave, guttaṃ mahato atthāya saṃvattatī”ti."
msgstr "A guarded mind is very beneficial.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an1.31-40:34.1.3"
msgid "Catutthaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p></article></section><section class="sutta" data-uid="an1.35" id="35"><article><div class="hgroup"><h1>
msgctxt "an1.31-40:34.1.4"
msgid "35"
msgstr "35"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc35.1"></a>
msgctxt "an1.31-40:35.1.1"
msgid ""
"“Nāhaṃ, bhikkhave, aññaṃ ekadhammampi samanupassāmi yaṃ evaṃ arakkhitaṃ "
"mahato anatthāya saṃvattati yathayidaṃ, bhikkhave, cittaṃ."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, I do not see a single thing that, when it’s not protected, is "
"so very harmful as the mind."

msgctxt "an1.31-40:35.1.2"
msgid "Cittaṃ, bhikkhave, arakkhitaṃ mahato anatthāya saṃvattatī”ti."
msgstr "An unprotected mind is very harmful.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an1.31-40:35.1.3"
msgid "Pañcamaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p></article></section><section class="sutta" data-uid="an1.36" id="36"><article><div class="hgroup"><h1>
msgctxt "an1.31-40:35.1.4"
msgid "36"
msgstr "36"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc36.1"></a>
msgctxt "an1.31-40:36.1.1"
msgid ""
"“Nāhaṃ, bhikkhave, aññaṃ ekadhammampi samanupassāmi yaṃ evaṃ rakkhitaṃ "
"mahato atthāya saṃvattati yathayidaṃ, bhikkhave, cittaṃ."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, I do not see a single thing that, when it is protected, is so "
"very beneficial as the mind."

msgctxt "an1.31-40:36.1.2"
msgid "Cittaṃ, bhikkhave, rakkhitaṃ mahato atthāya saṃvattatī”ti."
msgstr "A protected mind is very beneficial.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an1.31-40:36.1.3"
msgid "Chaṭṭhaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p></article></section><section class="sutta" data-uid="an1.37" id="37"><article><div class="hgroup"><h1>
msgctxt "an1.31-40:36.1.4"
msgid "37"
msgstr "37"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc37.1"></a>
msgctxt "an1.31-40:37.1.1"
msgid ""
"“Nāhaṃ, bhikkhave, aññaṃ ekadhammampi samanupassāmi yaṃ evaṃ asaṃvutaṃ "
"mahato anatthāya saṃvattati yathayidaṃ, bhikkhave, cittaṃ."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, I do not see a single thing that, when it’s not restrained, is "
"so very harmful as the mind."

msgctxt "an1.31-40:37.1.2"
msgid "Cittaṃ, bhikkhave, asaṃvutaṃ mahato anatthāya saṃvattatī”ti."
msgstr "An unrestrained mind is very harmful.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an1.31-40:37.1.3"
msgid "Sattamaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p></article></section><section class="sutta" data-uid="an1.38" id="38"><article><div class="hgroup"><h1>
msgctxt "an1.31-40:37.1.4"
msgid "38"
msgstr "38"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc38.1"></a>
msgctxt "an1.31-40:38.1.1"
msgid ""
"“Nāhaṃ, bhikkhave, aññaṃ ekadhammampi samanupassāmi yaṃ evaṃ saṃvutaṃ mahato "
"atthāya saṃvattati yathayidaṃ, bhikkhave, cittaṃ."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, I do not see a single thing that, when it is restrained, is so "
"very beneficial as the mind."

msgctxt "an1.31-40:38.1.2"
msgid "Cittaṃ, bhikkhave, saṃvutaṃ mahato atthāya saṃvattatī”ti."
msgstr "A restrained mind is very beneficial.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an1.31-40:38.1.3"
msgid "Aṭṭhamaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p></article></section><section class="sutta" data-uid="an1.39" id="39"><article><div class="hgroup"><h1>
msgctxt "an1.31-40:38.1.4"
msgid "39"
msgstr "39"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc39.1"></a>
msgctxt "an1.31-40:39.1.1"
msgid ""
"“Nāhaṃ, bhikkhave, aññaṃ ekadhammampi samanupassāmi yaṃ evaṃ adantaṃ aguttaṃ "
"arakkhitaṃ asaṃvutaṃ mahato anatthāya saṃvattati yathayidaṃ, bhikkhave, "
"cittaṃ."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, I do not see a single thing that, when it is not tamed, "
"guarded, protected and restrained, is so very harmful as the mind."

msgctxt "an1.31-40:39.1.2"
msgid ""
"Cittaṃ, bhikkhave, adantaṃ aguttaṃ arakkhitaṃ asaṃvutaṃ mahato anatthāya "
"saṃvattatī”ti."
msgstr ""
"An untamed, unguarded, unprotected, and unrestrained mind is very harmful.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an1.31-40:39.1.3"
msgid "Navamaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p></article></section><section class="sutta" data-uid="an1.40" id="40"><article><div class="hgroup"><h1>
msgctxt "an1.31-40:39.1.4"
msgid "40"
msgstr "40"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc40.1"></a>
msgctxt "an1.31-40:40.1.1"
msgid ""
"“Nāhaṃ, bhikkhave, aññaṃ ekadhammampi samanupassāmi yaṃ evaṃ dantaṃ guttaṃ "
"rakkhitaṃ saṃvutaṃ mahato atthāya saṃvattati yathayidaṃ, bhikkhave, cittaṃ."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, I do not see a single thing that, when it is tamed, guarded, "
"protected and restrained, is so very beneficial as the mind."

msgctxt "an1.31-40:40.1.2"
msgid ""
"Cittaṃ, bhikkhave, dantaṃ guttaṃ rakkhitaṃ saṃvutaṃ mahato atthāya "
"saṃvattatī”ti."
msgstr "A tamed, guarded, protected, and restrained mind is very beneficial.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an1.31-40:40.1.3"
msgid "Dasamaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an1.31-40:40.1.4"
msgid "Adantavaggo catuttho."
msgstr ""
